          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今日里回家中得见娘亲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看在了父死早孤苦伶仃。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是孩儿胸无才错认书信"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "离膝下二十载埋名隐姓"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "虽则是儿不才胸无学问"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听一言我这里珠泪难忍，"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "骂一声不肖子大胆畜生。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "到后来成大贤领袖群伦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "到如今年三十一事无成。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "保玄德无始终万古骂名。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "倒不如早与我速速登程。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是孩儿胸无才错认书信"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "离膝下二十载埋名隐姓"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "虽则是儿不才胸无学问"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "畜生呵畜生！我也不来责备与你，你与我速速地去罢，哎呀！皇天呵皇天，我"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "徐门为何这等不幸？呵！也罢，我想这等不肖之子，我有何面目再见人，你与"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我速速地去，你与我速速地去呵！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（徐母哭下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "主人请起，老夫人进内堂去了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎！"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "母悲儿说得我抬头不起，"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "错中了奸雄计难以回头。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦！有了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且做个明保曹暗保汉自有神机。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（丫鬟上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀老爷不好了，老夫人在二堂自尽了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎么讲？"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老夫人二堂自尽了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，母亲呀，为什么寻此短见，兀的不痛煞我也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一阵阵痛煞我徐庶元直，"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为什么我的母自尽丧身。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "回家来害了母一命归阴。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（徐庶哭。众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
